<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 18:19:22 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>西尔弗表示，在争议之后他预计NBA比赛将重返中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/basketball/silver-says-he-expects-nba-games-will-return-china-after-controversy-2024-10-10/</link><description>亚当·萧华 (Adam Silver) 专员认为，NBA 可能会再次在中国举办比赛，五年前，香港民主抗议引发的争议引发了对北美顶级联赛的强烈反对。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 17:38:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/basketball/silver-says-he-expects-nba-games-will-return-china-after-controversy-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普提议将汽车贷款利息减税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-propose-making-car-loan-interest-tax-deductible-speech-2024-10-10/</link><description>根据路透社在底特律发表讲话之前的演讲摘录，共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普周四将提议将所有汽车贷款利息完全免税，并采取措施阻止中国汽车制造商在美国销售汽车。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 16:54:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-propose-making-car-loan-interest-tax-deductible-speech-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>韩国队击败约旦队在世界杯预选赛中保持不败</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/south-korea-down-jordan-remain-unbeaten-world-cup-qualifying-2024-10-10/</link><description>周四，在安曼举行的世界杯预选赛亚洲区第三轮比赛中，韩国队以2-0击败约旦队，以B组头名身份晋级，而澳大利亚队则在新任主帅托尼·波波维奇的带领下赢得了首场比赛的胜利。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 16:33:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/south-korea-down-jordan-remain-unbeaten-world-cup-qualifying-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯称“核五国”即将在纽约举行会议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-says-nuclear-five-states-meet-soon-new-york-2024-10-10/</link><description>俄罗斯官方媒体周四援引外交部副部长谢尔盖·里亚布科夫的话说，五个核武器国家小组将在未来两周内在纽约举行会议。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 15:01:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-says-nuclear-five-states-meet-soon-new-york-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>台湾称四名富士康员工在中国被拘留</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-four-foxconn-employees-detained-china-2024-10-10/</link><description>台湾政府表示，全球最大的 iPhone 组装商台湾富士康的四名员工在“相当奇怪”的情况下在中国被拘留。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 13:31:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-four-foxconn-employees-detained-china-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>克里姆林宫否认朝鲜士兵在乌克兰作战的报道</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/kremlin-dismisses-reports-north-korean-soldiers-fighting-ukraine-2024-10-10/</link><description>克里姆林宫周四驳回了韩国的说法，即朝鲜可能已派遣一些军事人员帮助俄罗斯对抗乌克兰，并可能正在考虑进行更大规模的部署。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 12:31:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/kremlin-dismisses-reports-north-korean-soldiers-fighting-ukraine-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚3-1战胜中国开启波波维奇时代</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/australia-start-popovic-era-with-3-1-win-over-china-2024-10-10/</link><description>周四，在阿德莱德椭圆形球场举行的世界杯预选赛中，澳大利亚队以 3-1 的比分战胜中国队，托尼·波波维奇作为澳大利亚队主教练取得了胜利的开局。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 11:59:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/australia-start-popovic-era-with-3-1-win-over-china-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>宜家呼吁中国采取更多刺激措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/ikea-calls-more-china-stimulus-measures-2024-10-10/</link><description>在中国政府宣布一揽子措施以重振遭受房地产危机打击的经济后，瑞典家具零售商宜家周四敦促中国采取进一步的刺激措施。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 11:05:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/ikea-calls-more-china-stimulus-measures-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>房地产市场疲软降价后宜家销售额下降 5%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/ikea-sales-fall-5-after-price-cuts-amid-weak-housing-market-2024-10-10/</link><description>瑞典廉价家居用品零售商宜家为了吸引更多购物者并维持其在不断萎缩的家居市场中的份额而降价，该公司的年销售额下降了 5%，但预计明年将出现复苏。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 11:03:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/ikea-sales-fall-5-after-price-cuts-amid-weak-housing-market-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>莱尼将向德国政府提交中国股权出售案</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/german-ministry-review-leoni-share-sale-chinese-firm-wiwo-reports-2024-10-10/</link><description>汽车供应商莱尼 (Leoni) 发言人周四表示，该公司正准备向德国政府登记将其多数股权出售给中国公司立讯精密 (Luxshare)，这被称为例行步骤。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 10:59:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/german-ministry-review-leoni-share-sale-chinese-firm-wiwo-reports-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国央行原副行长因受贿被判死刑缓期执行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/former-china-deputy-central-bank-head-gets-suspended-death-sentence-taking-2024-10-10/</link><description>官方媒体周四称，在金融业开展全面反腐运动之际，中国前央行副行长范一飞因受贿罪被判处死刑，缓期两年执行。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 09:53:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/former-china-deputy-central-bank-head-gets-suspended-death-sentence-taking-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>总理称中国将于年底前取消对澳大利亚龙虾的进口禁令</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-lift-ban-australian-lobster-imports-by-year-end-says-pm-2024-10-10/</link><description>澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴内塞周四表示，中国将在年底前恢复进口澳大利亚龙虾，这标志着长达四年的外交斗争的结束，这场斗争导致澳大利亚数百亿美元的出口被禁止进入中国。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 08:55:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-lift-ban-australian-lobster-imports-by-year-end-says-pm-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>随着全球需求降温，中国九月出口可能进一步放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-exports-likely-slowed-further-september-global-demand-cools-2024-10-10/</link><description>9月份中国出口增速可能为五个月来最慢，这表明制造商不再在几个贸易伙伴征收关税之前急于发出订单，而且全球对中国商品的需求正在疲软。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 08:07:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-exports-likely-slowed-further-september-global-demand-cools-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>袭击发生后中国将与巴基斯坦合作保护中国人员</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-work-with-pakistan-protect-chinese-personnel-following-attack-2024-10-10/</link><description>周日，一个分裂主义武装组织声称杀害了两名中国工程师，中国周四表示，将与巴基斯坦合作，保护中国在巴基斯坦的人员、项目和机构的安全。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 07:40:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-work-with-pakistan-protect-chinese-personnel-following-attack-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国奇瑞在西方竞争对手腾出的俄罗斯工厂组装汽车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-chery-assembles-cars-russian-plants-vacated-by-western-rivals-2024-10-10/</link><description>自入侵乌克兰以来，北京在俄罗斯不断变化的制造业格局和经济中发挥着越来越有影响力的作用。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 06:03:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-chery-assembles-cars-russian-plants-vacated-by-western-rivals-2024-10-10/</guid></item></channel></rss>